title: Episode 133: Feat. Jaquae
itunes:title: Episode 133: Feat. Jaquae
description:
On this weeks episode, Jaquae from Love and Hip Hop NY sits with ladies of Lip Service and speaks on a range of topics including what he foresees his wedding to be like, who he would dress up as in the bedroom, and much more! Jaquae even confessed he purchased his girl, Kiyanne, a promise ring before meeting her family! Side note...is there such thing as a favorite ex?
